name: r-geiger
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.0.10" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-geiger
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/geiger_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/geiger/geiger_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2895cfb73fb91764be2ec3f931e4f3b2e75ae00a1431af4b40dc90e7c0693be0

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  skip: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - libopenblas
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-rcpp >=0.11.0
    - r-coda
    - r-colorspace
    - r-desolve >=1.7
    - r-digest
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-ncbit
    - r-subplex
    - r-phytools >=0.7.31
  run:
    - libopenblas
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-mass
    - r-rcpp >=0.11.0
    - r-coda
    - r-colorspace
    - r-desolve >=1.7
    - r-digest
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-ncbit
    - r-subplex
    - r-phytools >=0.7.31

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('geiger')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('geiger')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://www.webpages.uidaho.edu/~lukeh/software.html
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Methods for fitting macroevolutionary models to phylogenetic trees.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - jenzopr

# Package: geiger
# Type: Package
# Title: Analysis of Evolutionary Diversification
# Version: 2.0.6.2
# Date: 2015-09-07
# Author: Luke Harmon <lukeh@uidaho.edu>, Jason Weir, Chad Brock, Rich Glor, Wendell Challenger, Gene Hunt, Rich FitzJohn, Matt Pennell, Graham Slater, Joseph Brown, Josef Uyeda, and Jon Eastman <jonathan.eastman@gmail.com>
# Maintainer: ORPHANED
# Depends: ape (>= 3.0-6), R (>= 2.15.0)
# Imports: MASS, mvtnorm, subplex, deSolve (>= 1.7), digest, Rcpp (>= 0.11.0), coda, ncbit, colorspace, methods
# LinkingTo: Rcpp
